description:
Participants are rewarded with exclusive access after hours at one of the Sunshine Coasts most iconic natural areas. While there are many options for frog spotting within the confines of this reserve, ECOllaboration selected the ephemeral wetlands trail to monitor frog diversity and abundance and has been surveying here since 2022.

The commencement of the 100m transect line is located at;
https://maps.app.goo.gl/Ugfh3LCNreoeTvaP7
